body_html:
Everything seems to be working fine with my local system or any of the EC instances on AWS that I spawn. I install conda and install pip on it, then install onnx from source and caffe2 from source

cmake -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=OFF -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX="/home/ec2-user/cf2/" -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH="/home/ec2-user/cf2/" -DUSE_GFLAGS=OFF ..

When I run the program on my linux machine it works fine. Then I use zappa to deploy it onto Lambda, that is where I see this issue.

body:
Everything seems to be working fine with my local system or any of the EC instances on AWS that I spawn. I install conda and install pip on it, then install onnx from source and caffe2 from source 

cmake -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=OFF -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX="/home/ec2-user/cf2/" -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH="/home/ec2-user/cf2/" -DUSE_GFLAGS=OFF  ..

When I run the program on my linux machine it works fine. Then I use zappa to deploy it onto Lambda, that is where I see this issue.
